<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
<div>
    <p>[Socials] ("we," "us," or "our") values your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and disclose information about you when you visit our website [socials.com] (the "Site") or otherwise interact with us. By using our Site, you agree to the terms outlined in this policy.</p>
</div>

