<div>
    <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <b>Personal Information: </b> This includes your name, email address, phone number, payment information, and other details you provide when filling out forms, making purchases, or contacting us.
        </li>
        <li>
            <b>Non-Personal Information: </b> This includes data such as your browser type, IP address, operating system, and browsing behavior on our Site.
        </li>
        <li>
            <b>Cookies and Tracking Technologies: </b> We may use cookies, web beacons, and other tracking technologies to enhance your browsing experience.
